channel.title: Project Fubergen Client [Lite version 1.0 ] Great Base
channel.description:
[b]Yes i am releasing the lite version, that is based off Project Fubergen v8.3.2. and this is open source, and it doesnt include hidden files [/b]
what news?
- no jtoolbar anymore, looks cleanier without jtoolbar's buttons and might be lil less laggy - Some new jframe commands, eg. choose object to click
Note: bankall doesnt work on all server, but usually on czars
note: music options in misc menu
the server was runelife, when i tested this client.
This client works greatly on deltas, shards, iclarity and devo based servers. This is great client to start building your own client.
[IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/25s0bd5.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i32.tinypic.com/f56mb9.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i30.tinypic.com/2r6p450.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i27.tinypic.com/1z6wrjt.png[/img]
[u][b]Download link[/b][/u] [url=http://www.fileshost.com/download.php?id=8B1EB5F31]http://www.fileshost.com/download.php?id=8B1EB5F31[/url]
http://uppit.com/v/W26J2TR8
Credits:
Fubergen[me] lol, Galkon Bluurs Webber = for jtabbedpane idea [ note: i didnt use his tab methods] Dan aka pur3pkftw SilentCJ for new d plate Ricscape client v8.5's factors Background created byIPhoenix Java tutorial from java! Globe for helping Cocoa Pennzoil Aka stepehi Enurscape For server's selection codes [I modified it for my client ] Danno - Most New jframe features from dannos client [i just non renamed them and modified for my client]
Client base PF v6 Original Base: ricscape v8.5
